name: Brown/black leather Xs bill-fold wallet
description:
Just in time for the holidays! For the men on your list to put in their pockets, or for the ladies to stick inside their small pouch!

This is a simple leather wallet, with a compartment for cash, and 2 smaller compartments for cards. 

Made in the USA by me! Made of natural cow hide, thick and strong enough to hold your most valuables. Printed with ARC of LA signature Xs in black. Block-printed paint ages beautifully with the leather and becomes part of the patina.
